snippet.title: Love Spell: Written In The Stars [Kickstarter Launch Video]
snippet.description:
"Love Spell: Written In The Stars" is a romantic comedy visual novel/otome game about spells, adventures, penguins and the greatest magic of all: true love! 

It is the debut project of Great Gretuski Studios LLC, a female-founded, female-run indie game development studio focused on bringing romantic & creative stories to life.

♡ AVAILABLE NOW ON STEAM, ITCHIO OR GAMEJOLT ♡ 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1250520/Love_Spell_Written_In_The_Stars/
https://gretuskigames.itch.io/love-spell-written-in-the-stars
https://gamejolt.com/games/lovespell/519581
